name: SERIBUPATI CAMP
address: P39V+2CQ, Munduk, Banjar, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81152, Indonesia
review 1: Paradies Camping Place in a Plantage. Very quite and nice mountain and lake view! As well good sanitary place
review 2: This place is so nice. Amazing views, like camping in the clouds. Brought the family up here. Was a tough, we brought too much stuff, but everyone was so ready to help. Once we got setup was amazing, just wish we stayed longer.

name: Coffee-ology by Women's Co-ops
address: P39Q+F9, Munduk, Banjar, Buleleng Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: Great experience with the local Farmers ! Quality coffee tour with broad knowledged-local guide, uniq traditional coffee processing and of course having coffee itself. The view from the hut is splendid too. Just reserve the tour in advance vis the WA. Recommended
review 2:
Nowhere but here
Coffee tour by the local coops is amazing and worth supporting. Coffee processing and tasting is also amazing. Reserve in advance for the tour

Recommended
review 3: Great Coffee tour by great local guide for a great coffee but must reserve firt for the tour
